data.description: This end unit townhouse is located in the center of Carson City minutes away from downtown where you'll enjoy shopping, dining, and entertainment. The freeways to Reno, Lake Tahoe, and Minden are nearby as well. Stackable washer and dryer located upstairs between the two spacious bedrooms and the full bath that is finished with tasteful tile and other modern finishes. The galley kitchen has upgraded appliances. There is a private patio and a detached 1 car garage. The carpet was cleaned on November 11, 2023 To view this property please text or call Listing Agent. Showing times are Monday through Friday 8AM to 1:30PM. All day Saturday and Sunday. Please give at least 30 minutes notice.
